  "description": "Personal agent operating system. Hook layer + safety guards + workflow rules for AI assistants.",
  "status": "runtime-imported",
  "import_notes": [
    "v1.3.27 \u2014 Phase 10 level-up: security skill pack (red-team-check, blue-team-fix, purple-team-report, security-scope-gate, anti-fake-pass-gate, /security-scan), skill standard infrastructure (skill-spec, skill-writing-guide, skill-evaluation-rules, SKILL_TEMPLATE), design/UX skill pack (design-taste-frontend, image-to-code, ui-redesign, output-enforcement, minimalist-ui, ui-quality-gate), model-routing-strategy. Sources: ECC MIT, Strix Apache 2.0, Taste-skill MIT, Free-claude-code MIT, AgentSkills Apache 2.0. commands 155\u2192156, skills 65\u219273, templates 11\u219212.",
    "v1.3.26 \u2014 count sync + new hooks + new skill: commands 152\u2192155 (output-budget, output-raw, session-cost + 11 unlisted v1.3.24 commands), scripts 20\u219221 (session-cost.sh), hooks 24\u219226 (session-bootstrap.sh UserPromptSubmit, permission-auto-approve.sh PermissionRequest), skills 64\u219265 (l1-promote), templates 11\u219210, rules actual_present completed to all 11 files. Output Budget Layer: docs/OUTPUT_BUDGET_POLICY.md, docs/OUTPUT_BUDGET_INTEGRATION.md, session-bootstrap injects L1 facts into every prompt.",
    "v1.3.25-clean \u2014 metadata sync: plugin.json + marketplace.json counts (87 agents/152 commands/64 skills/123 checks/58 skill triggers), MANIFEST releases index corrected (latest \u2192 v1.3.24, files list fixed), docs version bump (all \u2192 1.3.25-clean), run-hook-tests.sh banner v1.3.15 \u2192 v1.3.25.",
    "v1.3.24 \u2014 Phase 9 import from sangrokjung/claude-forge (MIT): 4 agents (build-error-resolver, verify-agent, planner, database-reviewer), 11 commands (handoff-verify, commit-push-pr, refactor-clean, sync-docs, quick-commit, worktree-start, worktree-cleanup, eval, suggest-automation, learn, next-task), 13 skills (team-orchestrator, strategic-compact, session-wrap, verification-engine, skill-factory, security-compliance, security-pipeline, stride-analysis-patterns, debugging-strategies, extract-errors, build-system, cache-components, verify-implementation), 6 rules (golden-principles, verification, security, git-workflow-v2, testing, agents-v2). Phase 9 also: 2 karanb192-inspired skills (hook-block-commands, hook-protect-secrets).",
    "v1.3.23-clean \u2014 metadata/docs sync: plugin.json + marketplace.json counts (83 agents/141 commands/49 skills/108 checks), docs version bump (ARCHITECTURE/HOOK_WIRING/MAINTENANCE_POLICY/CLAUDE_MD_GUIDE \u2192 1.3.23-clean), README fix (42\u219283 agents), verify-skills-lock.sh + update-skills-lock.sh path fallback (scaffold vs installed), release zip policy added to MAINTENANCE_POLICY.",
    "v1.3.22 \u2014 Phase 8 import: 9 skills from alirezarezvani/claude-skills (agenthub, write-a-skill, handoff, caveman, code-tour, chaos-engineering, llm-cost-optimizer, pulse, research) + 2 YAMTAM-native skills (session-context, pre-compact-backup from disler patterns). hook-review.md false-positive fix (exclude core/commands/ from bypass scan).",
    "v1.3.21 \u2014 Conflict Resolution Policy: multi-agent edit conflict detection, priority rules (safety > correctness > performance > style), resolution strategies (sequential/merge/human escalation), conflict log format.",
    "v1.3.20 \u2014 YAMTAM-native skills: telemetry-analysis (audit log + hook activity analysis) + subagent-dependency (DAG-based multi-agent orchestration). Governance layer expansion.",
    "Phase 7 import completed 2026-05-19 from wshobson/commands. Added: 45 commands (tools x34, workflows x11). Generic workflow tools, no product dependencies.",
    "Phase 6 import completed 2026-05-19 from rohitg00/awesome-claude-code-toolkit + affaan-m/everything-claude-code. Added: 41 agents (core-development x8, quality-assurance x6, infrastructure x8, business x4, data-ai x6, orchestration x3, dev-experience x4, research x2). Added: 22 commands (git x5, devops x3, architecture x4, refactoring x4, security x2, testing x3, workflow x1). Added: 12 skills (api-design, backend-patterns, coding-standards, deep-research, documentation-lookup, e2e-testing, security-review, tdd-workflow, verification-loop, agent-introspection-debugging, frontend-patterns, mcp-server-patterns).",
    "Phase 5 import completed 2026-05-19 from qdhenry/Claude-Command-Suite. Added: 23 agents (architecture-auditor, code-auditor, dependency-analyzer, performance-auditor, infrastructure x4, quality-testing x5, security-auditor, task-orchestration x3, strategic/release/project management x6, agent-organizer). Added: 41 commands (security x4, dev x11, test x4, performance x4, docs x5, team x6, project x3, deploy x3, context x1). Added: 4 skills (audit-env-variables, remove-dead-code, file-watcher, setup-agent-tail). Generic workflow tools, no product dependencies.",
    "v1.3.16 \u2014 Claude Code Harness integration: maintenance policy, CLAUDE.md architecture guide, subagent read-only policy, LSP navigation skill, hook-review command.",
    "Phase 4 import completed 2026-05-18 from jnmt-claude-code-agenl-21 (internal). Added: checkpoint and handoff commands. Generic workflow tools, no product dependencies.",
    "Phase 3 import completed 2026-05-18 from glebis/claude-skills (MIT License). Adapted: tdd skill (RED\u2192GREEN\u2192REFACTOR, multi-agent context isolation). External scripts removed, integrated with verify-before-done and debug-protocol skills.",
    "Phase 2 import completed 2026-05-18 from superpowers v5.1.0 (MIT License, obra/superpowers). Adapted: plan-first, verify-before-done, debug-protocol, branch-finish, worktree-safety skills + diff-review command. Content rewritten in YAMTAM style \u2014 not copied verbatim.",
    "Phase 1 safe import completed 2026-05-17 from jnmt-claude-code-agenl-21 workshop repo.",
    "Excluded: react-native-developer.md, copywriter-seo.md, settings.json (pending content review).",
    "Excluded: memory/checkpoint/brain-dump/handoff commands, hooks, and scripts.",
    "Excluded: all JNMT product code, secrets, state logs, and zip files.",
